gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

This you will do, You will have billions of prosperity; 
This you will behave like two brothers, Take heed to my word and consider it true.

This is the translation:

That dharma is for truth and liberation, know it well; 
There is no doubt in this matter, consider it settled.

Here is the translation:

Arrived at the doorstep of my own person, there my true self is ruined; 
Thinking deeply, a matter was settled, then all worldly actions were finished.

The deer's game is tied with the sacred basil; 
Uppermost sign of great expansion is seen.
Mythical knot on the head, secured by a staff of a palm tree's trunk.

Here is the translation:

Four sciences are good which are in his book, its pages beautifully adorned; 
Make a rope of myrtle twigs and beg at someone's door, it is suitable for alms.

Here is the translation:

Ran fiercely in great speed, and then the demon was killed; 
If you go far away seeing him, then you will get scolded afterwards, and the wicked one will look at you with envy.
